summary: Looking at the new episode of Moominvalley, and the previous ep as well, this show has great comedy. Not only visual gags and...
body: Looking at the new episode of Moominvalley, and the previous ep as well, this show has great comedy. Not only visual gags and jokes, but with this ep the music rlly drives it too. I laughed everytime the background music changed when the Mameluke appeared. The more I watch this show the more love I feel for Tove Jansson and how thoughtful and loving this show is when it comes to its treatment of the Moomins
